<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.4">
<l>kañcaṉ ṟaṉṉāṟ puṇarkkap paṭṭa kaḷḷac cakaṭu kalakka ḻiyap</l>
<l>pañci yaṉṉa mella ṭiyāṟ pāynta pōtu nonti ṭummeṉ</l>
<l>ṟañci ṉēṉkā ṇamarar kōvē yāyar kūṭṭat taḷavaṉ ṟālō</l>
<l>kañca ṉaiyuṉ vañca ṉaiyāl valaippa ṭuttāy mulaiyu ṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look! I feared that you would suffer</l>
<l>when you attacked the treacherous cart</l>
<l rend="indent">that had been created by Kaṃsa</l>
<l>with your tender, cotton-like feet so that it was shattered and ruined.</l>
<l>King of immortals! You who caught Kaṃsa with your own deceit,</l>
<l rend="indent">there was no limit to the [fear of] the herder clan that day.</l>
<l>Drink from [my] breast!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
